## 1. 统一返回结果 R.java（common包）
```java
@Data
public class R<T> {
    private int code;
    private String msg;
    private T data;

    public static <T> R<T> ok(T data) {
        R<T> r = new R<>();
        r.code = 200;
        r.msg = "成功";
        r.data = data;
        return r;
    }
    public static <T> R<T> fail(String msg) {
        R<T> r = new R<>();
        r.code = 500;
        r.msg = msg;
        return r;
    }
}
```

## 2. 用户实体 User.java（entity）
```java
